---
title: Iva Hujerová - PPC specialista, analytika, marketingové strategie
description: Specializuji se na online marketing pro malé a střední firmy. Věnuji se PPC kampaním, analytice a SEO. Nabízím nastavení kampaní, audit i školení.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">

    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

        <title>{{ title }} | IvaHu.cz</title>
        <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
        <meta property="og:url" content="{{ baseUrl }}{{ page.url }}"/>
        <meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }} | IvaHu.cz"/>
        <meta property="og:description" content="{{ description }}"/>
        <meta property="og:image" content="{{ baseUrl }}/assets/fb-share.png"/>
        <meta property="og:locale" content="cs_CZ"/>

        <!-- Google Tag Manager -->
        <script>(function (w, d, s, l, i) {
                w[l] = w[l] || [];
                w[l].push({
                    'gtm.start':
                        new Date().getTime(), event: 'gtm.js'
                });
